description:
The Complete Series from Award-Winning producer/director, Ken Burns entitled &quot;The War&quot;

Contains 7 parts detailing the followings of folks in 4 American towns, that each had those fighting &amp; those staying home to keep the &quot;War Machine&quot; going. First-hand accounts largely litter the landscape for us to follow &amp; is surely what makes this series one of Ken Burns' best.


Pt 1) &quot;A Necessary War

Pt 2) &quot;When Things Get Tough&quot;

Pt 3) &quot;A Deadly Calling&quot;

Pt 4) &quot;Pride of Our Nation&quot;

Pt 5) &quot;FUBAR&quot;

Pt 6) &quot;The Ghost Front&quot;

Pt 7) &quot;A World Without War&quot;


Enjoy!!
